     On April 24, 2003, Amazon.com, Inc. announced its first quarter 2003 financial results. A copy of the press release containing the announcement is included as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K and is incorporated herein by reference. The foregoing information is provided pursuant to Item 9, "Regulation FD Disclosure," and Item 12, "Results of Operations and Financial Condition," on Form 8-K.
