ITEM 2.02. RESULTS OF OPERATIONS AND FINANCIAL CONDITION
 
On October 21, 2004, Amazon.com, Inc. announced its third quarter 2004 financial results. A copy of the press release containing the announcement is included as Exhibit 99.1 and additional information regarding non-GAAP financial measures included in certain of Amazon.com's public disclosures, including its third quarter 2004 financial results announcement, is included as Exhibit 99.2. Both of these exhibits are incorporated herein by reference.
