ITEM 2.02. RESULTS OF OPERATIONS AND FINANCIAL CONDITION
 
On February 2, 2005, Amazon.com, Inc. announced its fourth quarter 2004 and year ended December 31, 2004 financial results. A copy of the press release containing the announcement is included as Exhibit 99.1 and additional information regarding non-GAAP financial measures included in certain of Amazon.com's public disclosures, including its fourth quarter 2004 and year ended December 31, 2004 financial results announcement, is included as Exhibit 99.2. Both of these exhibits are incorporated herein by reference.
