On March 19, 2007, Mark Peek resigned his position as the Company's principal accounting officer, effective April 15, 2007. Mr. Peek has accepted the position of Chief Financial Officer at VMware, Inc.
On March 21, 2007, the Company appointed Shelley Reynolds, the Company's Vice President, Finance and Controller, as the Company's principal accounting officer, effective following Mr. Peek's termination of employment.
Ms. Reynolds, age 42, has been the Company's Controller since joining the Company in February 2006 and previously had been a partner at Deloitte & Touche LLP since 1998.
 
