ITEM 7.01. REGULATION FD DISCLOSURE.
On November 8, 2010, Amazon.com, Inc. announced that it had agreed to acquire Quidsi, Inc. A copy of the press release containing the announcement is included as Exhibit 99.l.
ITEM 9.01. FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND EXHIBITS.
(d) Exhibits.
 
 
