ITEM 2.02.  RESULTS OF OPERATIONS AND FINANCIAL CONDITION.
On January 31, 2012, Amazon.com, Inc. announced its fourth quarter 2011 and year ended December 31, 2011 financial results. A copy of the press release containing the announcement is included as Exhibit 99.1 and additional information regarding the inclusion of non-GAAP financial measures in certain of Amazon.com's public disclosures, including its fourth quarter 2011 and year ended December 31, 2011 financial results announcement, is included as Exhibit 99.2. Both of these exhibits are incorporated herein by reference.
